{"tid":689412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國領航鯨死亡 體內塞滿80個膠袋","createTime":"2018-06-04T05:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T05:38:48.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"812559be3df8776659422dac688d1c912641a769","tid":689412,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpWrw87s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpWrw87s.jpg&h=c72e1adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">解剖後赫然發現，牠胃裡竟有重達8公斤的80個塑膠袋，解剖畫面曝光令人震驚。（路透）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕泰國南方靠近馬來西亞邊界日前出現一條雄性領航鯨，這頭幼鯨奄奄一息，雖然救援人員試圖幫助牠漂浮，並為其搭建遮陽傘，但仍在1日下午死亡，過程中曾掙扎吐出5個塑膠袋，解剖赫然發現，這頭領航鯨胃裡有重達8公斤的80個塑膠袋，令人震驚。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，這又是一起的海洋生物誤食塑膠垃圾奪命最新案例，這頭雄性的領航鯨幼崽在泰國和馬來西亞邊界的一條運河中被發現，儘管救難人員盡全力搶救，最終領航鯨仍回天乏術，在救援期間，牠曾吐出5個塑膠袋，解剖後赫然發現，牠胃裡竟有重達8公斤的80個塑膠袋，解剖畫面曝光令人震驚。<br />\n<br />\n網友紛紛對牠的命運表達同情與憤怒，泰國農業大學（Kasetsart University）海洋生物學家那瓦沙瓦（Thon Thamrongnawasawat）指出，塑膠袋使這頭鯨魚無法吃進任何有營養的食物，「如果你胃裡有80個塑料袋，你也會死。」<br />\n<br />\n那瓦沙瓦透露，每年最少有300頭海洋生物，包括領航鯨、海龜和海豚等，在泰國水域因為吞下塑膠垃圾死亡，強調「這是個大問題，我們用太多塑料製品。」據了解，泰國是全球使用最多塑料袋的國家之一，當局近日表示，考慮隨袋徵稅以改善濫用情況，統計顯示，全球每年有800萬噸塑料排入海洋，進入野生動物食物鏈。。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php8hOJtp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php8hOJtp.jpg&h=0107d7f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpCMryC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpCMryC9.jpg&h=c010f3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2446836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2446836&d=kdpm3TGC%2FPzajP3Vx6HhkPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=97dc01dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2446836&h=be60ffcc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2446836</a>"},{"pid":"9b163a0c52640db1214bf5e20ff91a03de4bf012","tid":689412,"uid":20291,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:22:50.000Z","msg":"好想喊"},{"pid":"856344c7e1ddd406c86fd3c4e2928e608e0ad5eb","tid":689412,"uid":4597,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"養多幾條鯨魚咪可以清乾淨個海洋"},{"pid":"547677ffa1090c07101eca5a827dfa64bc2b9308","tid":689412,"uid":14830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"856344c7e1ddd406c86fd3c4e2928e608e0ad5eb","tid":689412,"uid":4597,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"養多幾條鯨魚咪可以清乾淨個海洋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b638edfbf9e1ffc0fabd22fa23ade98f47cd6873","tid":689412,"uid":61653,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"856344c7e1ddd406c86fd3c4e2928e608e0ad5eb","tid":689412,"uid":4597,"like":3,"d